<item>
            <title>[HBASE-6373] Add more context information to audit log messages</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-6373</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The attached patch adds more information to the audit log messages; namely, it includes the IP address where the request originated, if it&apos;s available.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The patch is against trunk, but I&apos;ve tested it against the 0.92 branch. I didn&apos;t find any unit test for this code, please let me know if I missed something.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
